      </p>
      <p><strong>Additional resources:</strong> the information about the conference will be made available on the <a class="link underline" href="https://scievent.urfu.ru/rcct2026">university website</a></p>
      <p><strong>Mass mail:</strong> the conference newsletters will be sent via the email (from @rcct2026.ru or @urfu.email). The subscription to the newsletter is available by request only. You can unsubscribe by sending an empty letter with "unsubscribe conferenceusu" (without quotes) as the email subject to <a class="link underline" href="mailto:sympa@urfu.email?subject=unsubscribe%20conferenceusu">sympa@urfu.email</a>.</p>
      <p><strong>Postal address:</strong> 620000, Ekaterinburg, 51 Lenin av., Ural Federal University, Institute of Natural Sciences and Mathematics, Department of Physical and Inorganic Chemistry</p>
